description.en: B8 is a token based on the BSC public chain. The project is mainly used for casino games. B8 plays the role of a bargaining chip in the game. It is circulated and sold in the game. Holding B8 can enjoy a 6% dividend, which is written into the contract. Ownership has been given up. The B8 team hopes to combine tokens and games to realize real value and give digital currency a place in playing and earning games.
